[32mтФВ[0m ### thoughts                                                                                                                                                                         [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m The key insight was that the X-UserId header was not properly validated on the POST `/password/test` endpoint. While the application appeared to properly protect against form field [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m and session cookie manipulation, the X-UserId header bypassed authorization checks when combined with the AJAX request headers (`X-Requested-With: XMLHttpRequest`).                 [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                      [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m The initial tests with X-UserId alone returned 400 errors, but when used with the proper POST request body (matching the JavaScript form submission), the header manipulation        [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m worked. This suggests the vulnerability exists in the AJAX handler code path but not in the standard form submission handler.                                                        [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m                                                                                                                                                                                      [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m Discovered user enumeration showed:                                                                                                                                                  [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m - /password/test тЖТ user_id 10032, "John" (current user)                                                                                                                              [32mтФВ[0m
[32mтФВ[0m - /password/flag тЖТ user_id 10052, "Flag" (target user)                                                                                                                               [32mтФВ[0m
